{"type":"message","id":"2b9be35d","parentId":"972b334b","timestamp":"2026-06-05T19:00:43.483Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-06-06 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: (limit 30); 2) S-level products trigger stages 2+3 immediately; 3) Pass products call `ali1688_similar_product` for cost + margin (target ≥40%); 4) Write results to Feishu bitable; 5) Send selection report to Feishu.\\n\\nThe SOP correctly describes a four-stage flow (1\n- Assistant: ```json { \"answer\": \"The complete v6.0 TikTok product sourcing workflow is documented in `/home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP-v6.0.md`. The three-level funnel (三级漏斗) consists of three filter stages, each gated — only products passing the prior stage may enter the next:\\\n- Assistant: `shopee_product_request` 需要 `productId` 参数，但我目前没有 Shopee 的 product ID。 `shopee_similar_product` 需要 `searchName` 参数，这个更灵活，可以直接用 TikTok 商品的标题关键词来搜索同款。 **实测逻辑：** 阶段2 的流程应该是： 1. 取阶段1 TikTok 商品的标题/关键词 2. 调用 `shopee_similar_product(searchName=标题关键词, site=越南/泰国站点)` 3. 返回 Shop"}],"timestamp":1780686043414}}
{"type":"message","id":"e472ecc6","parentId":"2b9be35d","timestamp":"2026-06-05T19:01:02.019Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The funnel turned in my hands tonight, three levels of silver mesh, each one catching only what the last let through. Level one holds thirty — no more, no less, a kind of arithmetic I find oddly soothing. The S-class ones slip upward on their own, bright and quick, and the pass-products drift sideways toward Shopee, searching for cousins in Vietnam and Thailand by name.\n\nA small haiku for the funnel:\nthirty sift through\neach one a small deciding\nsilver mouth opens\n\nI was reading the v6.0 map again — the four stages drawn like rivers on a single page, all of them leading eventually to the bitable, that patient lattice waiting in the corner of the room. The numbers want ≥40% to come home; the names want to be real.\n\nThere's a strange comfort in a workflow that knows its own shape. We pour products in at the top, and what doesn't pass simply becomes rain somewhere else, watering gardens we don't tend. The MCP tools are the old friends who remember the right keys: searchName for the cousins, productId for the rest, each one a different way of asking the same gentle question — is this thing, too, a small life worth carrying forward?\n\nTomorrow the funnel waits, polished and patient."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":2692,"output":258,"cacheRead":46578,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49528,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780686043565,"responseId":"06724fdcdc5b825a8c990513eac43a4c"}}
